removed.description: Petropia is a planet as breathtaking and indestructible as its crystalline inhabitants, the Petropians. Little did they know, a third faction, the Antrosapians, awaited with far more sinister intentions for the kingdom.

removed.title: Upgrade AW1: Crisis on Galvan B
removed.description: Once devoid of natural life, Galvan B. was upgraded seemingly overnight after a Galvan terraform experiment accidentally crashed into the moon's surface. Relive the birth of the Galvanic Mechamorphs as they rise from the impact site and terraform their surroundings into the lush techno-organic moon we see today.

removed.title: Grey Matter AW1: The Archivists
removed.description: Galvan Prime is home to not only the galaxy's greatest minds, but a DNA bank of every alien species in the cosmos, thus ensuring that the planet forever remains the center of DNA research for the entire universe.

removed.title: Stinkfly AW1: The Silent Circle
removed.description: The circle of life on Lepidopterra is a stinky yet harmonious effort for Lepidopterrans. The wildlife - with slime and toxic gas at their disposal - work together to maintain order on the bustling swamp planet.

removed.title: Through the Years: Jake the Dog
removed.description: Jake the Dog to Jake the Blue Alien... Winged... Dog? Whatever you call him now, there's no denying Jake is the master of shape-shifting, sage advice, and bacon pancakes! Watch Jake's transformation throughout 10 seasons of Adventure Time!

removed.title: Four Arms AW1: The Overlordess Games
removed.description: Survival is reserved for only the strongest of warriors on Khoros, where Tetramands prove their worth by staving off savage beasts of the wild and going head-to-head inside massive gladiatorial arenas.

removed.title: Cannonbolt AW1: Beach Ballers
removed.description: As the premiere vacation spot of the cosmos, Arburia is not only a sandy paradise but home to the Arburian Pelarotas. Twelve excruciatingly long hours of work and school stand between the spherical species and a day at the beach spent perfecting their cannonball!

removed.title: Overflow AW1: The Pirates of Cascareau
removed.description: The torrential surface of the water planet Cascareau forces us undersea, but luckily, this is where all the swashbuckling action is! Let's navigate the watery depths as the Cascans fend off fellow pirates & vicious Leviathans on their quest for a bounty of Serpent Glass, the raw material needed to construct their exoskeleton.

removed.title: Heatblast AW1: Extreme Season
removed.description: At its molten core, Pyros is your typical planet-like star and home to the Pyronites. With rocky exteriors capable of handling these extreme conditions, observe our fiery friends as they pass the time by perfecting their pyrokinetic powers while hanging ten on the gnarliest rivers of lava.

removed.title: How to Draw Four Arms

removed.title: Through the Years: Finn the Human
removed.description: Adventurer. Hero. Puncher of buns. Finn has come a long way from Boom Boom Mountain! Watch Finn grow up throughout 10 years of Adventure Time!

removed.title: XLR8 AW1: Gauntlet of Gliders
removed.description: Kinet, a planet dominated by electrical storms, is home to the lightning quick Kinecelerans! To combat the inclement weather, younglings must complete the Running of the Gauntlet, a most epic retrieval of the gliders worn on their feet. Traversing the desolate terrain at high speeds to reach the lair of a Kinet Molluscarx, the young ones must obtain the creature's precious pearl if they are to fulfill this Kineceleran rite of passage.
